  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introdução a Cdrtools</title>

    <para>
      The <application>Cdrtools</application> package contains CD recording
utilities. These are useful for reading, creating or writing (burning) CDs,
DVDs, and Blu-ray discs.
    </para>

    &lfs113_checked;

